      <div class="wheel-caption">The ring shows roughly where you are in your cycle — menstrual, follicular, ovulation, and luteal phases.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-grid" id="statGrid"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <span class="section-label">Looking ahead</span>
