  </div>

  <!-- HEALTH PROFILE TOGGLES -->
  <div class="card">
    <span class="section-label">Optional, just for you</span>
    <h2>Anything else you'd like extra support with?</h2>
    <div class="sub">Turning one on adds a gentle tracker for it below, plus notes on how it can interact with your cycle. Nothing here is shown unless you choose it.</div>
    <div class="toggle-row">
      <label class="toggle-chip" id="chip-diabetes"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-diabetes" onchange="toggleCondition('diabetes')"> 🩸 Diabetes</label>
      <label class="toggle-chip" id="chip-thyroid"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-thyroid" onchange="toggleCondition('thyroid')"> 🦋 Thyroid</label>
      <label class="toggle-chip" id="chip-asthma"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-asthma" onchange="toggleCondition('asthma')"> 🌬️ Asthma</label>
      <label class="toggle-chip" id="chip-pcos"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-pcos" onchange="toggleCondition('pcos')"> 🌸 PCOS/PCOD</label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- DIABETES -->
  <div class="card cond-card cond-reveal diabetes" id="section-diabetes" style="display:none;">
    <span class="pill mint" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Diabetes</span>
    <h2>Blood glucose tracker</h2>
    <div class="sub">High or unstable blood sugar can worsen insulin resistance, which is closely tied to irregular cycles and PCOS/PCOD.</div>
    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="field">
        <label for="d-date">Date</label>
        <input type="date" id="d-date">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="d-type">Reading type</label>
        <select id="d-type">
          <option value="Fasting">Fasting</option>
          <option value="Post-meal">Post-meal</option>
          <option value="Random">Random</option>
          <option value="HbA1c">HbA1c (%)</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="d-value">Value</label>
